ces because, though blighted by sin, they remain gifts from God.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aBaptism. 0aChristian life. 0aChristianityxCustoms and practices. 0aGiftsxReligious aspectsxChristianity. 0aLord's Supper. 0aMercantile systemzGermanyxHistoryy17th century. 0aMercantile systemzGermanyxHistoryy18th century. 0aPrayerxChristianity. 0aSinxChristianity. 0aSpiritual lifexChristianity. 7aRELIGION / Christian Theology / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018 Englishz978311060403008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311063899840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300241167?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300241167423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300241167/original  a978-3-11-060403-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-063899-8  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017